\c 10
\s Ukwehlulwa kwamaAmoni lamaSiriya
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho\x + 1 Lan. 19.1-19.\x* inkosi yabantwana bakoAmoni yafa, uHanuni indodana yayo wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sayo\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*.
\v 2 UDavida wasesithi: Ngizamenzela umusa uHanuni indodana kaNahashi njengoba uyise wangenzela umusa. UDavida wasethuma ngesandla senceku zakhe ukuyamduduza ngoyise\x + 9.1.\x*. Zafika-ke izinceku zikaDavida elizweni labantwana bakoAmoni.
\v 3 Iziphathamandla zabantwana bakoAmoni zasezisithi kuHanuni inkosi yazo: Kambe uDavida uyamhlonipha uyihlo emehlweni akho ngoba ethume abaduduzi kuwe? UDavida kazithumanga yini inceku zakhe kuwe ukuze ziphenye umuzi, ziwuhlole, ziwuchithe?
\v 4 UHanuni wasebamba izinceku zikaDavida, wagela ingxenye yendevu zazo, waquma izembatho zazo phakathi kuze kube sezibunu zazo, waziyekela zahamba\x + Isa. 20.4.\x*.
\v 5 Sebembikele uDavida wathumela ukuzihlangabeza ngoba amadoda ayelenhloni kakhulu; inkosi yasisithi: Hlalani eJeriko zize zihlume indevu zenu, beselibuya.
\p
\v 6 Lapho abantwana bakoAmoni sebebonile ukuthi baba levumba kuDavida\x + 16.21. 1 Sam. 13.4.\x*, abantwana bakoAmoni bathumela baqhatsha kumaSiriya\x + Hlu. 18.28.\x* eBeti-Rehobi\x + Hlu. 18.28.\x* lakumaSiriya eZoba, amadoda ahamba ngenyawo azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili\x + 8.3,5.\x*, lenkosini yeMahaka\x + 10.8. 23.34. Josh. 13.11,13. 1 Lan. 19.6,7. Dute. 3.14.\x*, amadoda ayinkulungwane, lebantwini beTobi, amadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili.
\v 7 Kwathi uDavida esekuzwile wathuma uJowabi lebutho lonke lamaqhawe\x + 23.8.\x*.
\v 8 Abantwana bakoAmoni basebephuma bahlela impi emnyango wesango; lamaSiriya eZoba leRehobi, labantu beTobi leMahaka babebodwa egangeni.
\v 9 Lapho uJowabi ebona ukuthi impi ikhangele kuye ngaphambili langemuva, wakhetha kubo bonke abakhethiweyo koIsrayeli, wabahlela ukuthi bamelane lamaSiriya.
\v 10 Abaseleyo babantu wasebanikela esandleni sikaAbishayi umfowabo, owabahlela ukuthi bamelane labantwana bakoAmoni.
\v 11 Wasesithi: Uba amaSiriya elamandla kakhulu kulami, khona uzakuba lusizo kimi; kodwa uba abantwana bakoAmoni belamandla kakhulu kulawe, khona ngizakuza ukukusiza.
\v 12 Qina\x + Dute. 31.6.\x*, asiziqinise ngenxa yabantu bakithi, langenxa yemizi kaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 1 Sam. 4.9.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* kayenze okuhle emehlweni ayo\x + 1 Sam. 3.18.\x*.
\v 13 UJowabi wasesondela, labantu ababelaye, empini lamaSiriya; asebaleka phambi kwakhe.
\v 14 Lapho abantwana bakoAmoni bebona ukuthi amaSiriya ayabaleka, labo babaleka phambi kukaAbishayi, bangena emzini\x + 1 Sam. 26.6.\x*. UJowabi wasebuyela esuka ebantwaneni bakoAmoni, weza eJerusalema.
\p
\v 15 AmaSiriya esebonile ukuthi atshayiwe phambi kukaIsrayeli, abuthana ndawonye.
\v 16 UHadadezeri wasethumela, wakhupha amaSiriya ayengaphetsheya komfula, afika eHelamu, loShobaki induna yebutho likaHadadezeri phambi kwawo\x + 8.3.\x*.
\v 17 Lapho kubikelwa uDavida, wabuthanisa uIsrayeli wonke, wachapha iJordani, wafika eHelamu. AmaSiriya asezihlelela ukumelana loDavida, alwa laye.
\v 18 AmaSiriya asebaleka phambi kukaIsrayeli; uDavida wasetshaya kumaSiriya izinqola ezingamakhulu ayisikhombisa\x + 8.4.\x*, labagadi bamabhiza abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane, watshaya uShobaki induna yebutho, owafela lapho\x + 1 Lan. 19.18.\x*.
\v 19 Lapho wonke amakhosi, izinceku zikaHadadezeri, ebona ukuthi atshaywa phambi kukaIsrayeli, enza ukuthula loIsrayeli\x + Josh. 10.1,4.\x*, abakhonza. Ngakho amaSiriya esaba ukusiza abantwana bakoAmoni futhi\x + 8.6.\x*.
